## ğŸ¨ Features

- **Modern terminal menu:** OS-style boxed menu with centered text  
- **Multiple themes:** dark, light, blue, green, red, pink, gold, silver, and more  
- **File manager & terminal commands:** list, create, read, delete files/folders  
- **Applications:** Calculator, Game Manager, Web Browser, Task Manager  
- **Add-ons & Devices:** modular plugin system  
- **Lightweight & modular:** easily add new applications and functionalities  

